comment:
* This class holds a capture ID and its expected last regular, zslStill, and reprocess
 * frame number.

variables.name: mLastRegularFrameNumber
variables.comment: CaptureCallback.NO_FRAMES_CAPTURED if the request ID has no regular request.

variables.name: mLastReprocessFrameNumber
variables.comment: CaptureCallback.NO_FRAMES_CAPTURED if the request ID has no reprocess request.

variables.name: mLastZslStillFrameNumber
variables.comment: CaptureCallback.NO_FRAMES_CAPTURED if the request ID has no zsl request.

variables.name: mSequenceCompleted
variables.comment: Whether the sequence is completed. (only consider capture result)

variables.name: mInflightCompleted
variables.comment: Whether the inflight request is completed. (consider result, buffers, and notifies)

methods.name: public long getLastRegularFrameNumber()
methods.comment:
* Return the last regular frame number. Return CaptureCallback.NO_FRAMES_CAPTURED if
     * it contains no regular request.

methods.name: public long getLastReprocessFrameNumber()
methods.comment:
* Return the last reprocess frame number. Return CaptureCallback.NO_FRAMES_CAPTURED if
     * it contains no reprocess request.

methods.name: public long getLastZslStillFrameNumber()
methods.comment:
* Return the last ZslStill frame number. Return CaptureCallback.NO_FRAMES_CAPTURED if
     * it contains no Zsl request.

methods.name: public long getLastFrameNumber()
methods.comment: * Return the last frame number overall.

methods.name: public boolean isSequenceCompleted()
methods.comment: * Return whether the capture sequence is completed.

methods.name: public void markSequenceCompleted()
methods.comment: * Mark the capture sequence as completed.

methods.name: public boolean isInflightCompleted()
methods.comment: * Return whether the inflight capture is completed.

methods.name: public void markInflightCompleted()
methods.comment: * Mark the inflight capture as completed.
